rComments: Excellent prof. I had him twice. Gives high marks and willing to debate!!
He also gives take-home exam that are truly based on the readings.  It is not necessary to go to class and his classes are extremely boring.  Very easy to get a good grade.  Just do the readings:)
Interesting, but only tests you on the readings which gives a sense of pointlessness to his lectures. He actually told us not to take notes!! Loved listening to him, and a super nice man overall.

Good teacher, knows his stuff.no visual aids.he's very passionate about this subject & for women's rights. Tip: assume that every thing told in class is completly true(dont contradict)and you'll do just fine in exams. ps: read what he gives you and listen to what he says cause he's not one to lie.Other words:if he says answers are in book,they are!
